Our Management Team «  EnviroStar, Inc.Our Management Team – EnviroStar, Inc.              EnviroStar, Inc. FOR INFORMATION: 305.754.8676 Search for:  Menu Our Management TeamHome → Company Overview → Our Management Team Henry M. NahmadMr. Nahmad serves as Chairman, President, and Chief Executive Officer of the Company. Mr. Nahmad is a leader and entrepreneur with a long-term vision and a passion for buying and building businesses. He previously served as Chief Executive Officer of Chemstar Corp., a provider of food safety and sanitation solutions, where he led a growth effort that resulted in recognition as a North American leader in its market segment. Earlier in his career, Mr. Nahmad worked in various capacities at Watsco, Inc. (NYSE: WSO), the largest distributor of HVAC/R products in the world, where he gained intimate knowledge and valuable experience in the execution of the buy-and-build strategy. Mr. Nahmad earned a B.A. in Economics from the University of Texas and an MBA from Babson College. He is a member of the Young Presidents Organization and is an active member in charitable organizations.Michael S. SteinerMr. Steiner serves as Executive Vice President of the Company and as President of Steiner-Atlantic Corp., a Company business unit based in Miami, FL. Mr. Steiner is a second-generation entrepreneur and industry veteran who has been President of Steiner-Atlantic Corp. since 1988. During his tenure, Mr. Steiner led strategic growth efforts for Steiner-Atlantic and managed nearly every facet of its operation. His experience as leader and operator is a valuable asset to the Company. Mr. Steiner is a member of the Florida Bar, earned a B.S. in Finance from the University of South Florida, and a JD from the University of Miami.Dennis MackDennis Mack serves as Executive Vice President and as a Director of EnviroStar. Mr. Mack is also the founder and President of Western State Design; a position he has held since its inception in 1974. Mr. Mack is an industry veteran, who along with his partner and team, built Western State Design into the leading distributor of commercial and coin-operated laundry products on the west coast of the United States. He is widely respected amongst his industry peers as not only an entrepreneur with a keen sense for opportunities in and around the industry, but also an exceptional leader. In consideration of his professional achievements, extensive relationships, and ever-burning entrepreneurial spirit, Mr. Mack is an invaluable member of the EnviroStar Management Team.Tom MarksTom Marks serves as Executive Vice President of EnviroStar. Mr. Marks also serves as Executive Vice President at Western State Design, a wholly owned subsidiary, where he was a partner for over 15 years. Mr. Marks is widely recognized and responsible for developing and executing the growth strategies, which led to Western’s recognition as one of the foremost commercial and coin-operated laundry distributors in the United States. As a member of EnviroStar’s Management Team, Mr. Marks serves in the same capacities, but with an expanded and integral role in the execution of the Company’s long-term buy and build growth strategy.Venerando J. IndelicatoMr. Indelicato serves as Chief Financial Officer of the Company and has served in such capacity since 1998. Before that time, Mr. Indelicato was President and Chief Executive Officer of Metro Tel Corp. from 1967 until 1998. Mr. Indelicato earned his B.S. in Engineering from Hofstra University.Company OverviewOur HistoryOur Business StrategyOur Management TeamOur Board of Directors ©  EnviroStar, Inc., All Rights Reserved.
