About Envirostar Lighting, Inc.  
Distributor specializing in LED Retrofits & New Fixtures
Envirostar ensures a great product with a great price!  Our commercial and industrial lighting products include: the latest LED technology in retrofits and new fixtures, fluorescents, and more for indoor and outdoor lighting. Our products are ideal for offices, warehouses, parking garages, schools, hospitals, parking lots, street lights and other commercial projects.  The major OEM's we represent are Made in America Manufacturer's.
 
 
 





